Package: mschart
Type: Package
Title: Chart generation for Microsoft PowerPoint Documents
Version: 0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Gohel", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "david.gohel@ardata.fr"),
    person("YouGov", role = "fnd"))
Description: Create charts for 'Microsoft PowerPoint' and  'Microsoft Word' documents. 
  Functions are provided to let users create charts, modify and format their content. 
  It extends package 'officer' that does not contain any feature for 'Microsoft' native 
  charts production.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
